column5: WHOA!!! Love the pike porn!!  I waited to see if a part 2 was coming, and boy did it ever!  Great report!
Awesome collection of gators! u must have had a wicked apir of pike hands after that weekend!
NICE.  Enough smiles and slime to go around!
Great pics!  I could've done without all the text though

Well well.... lookie lookie.  That 45incher is a real beautay.  Glad you got the posting thing figured out my fellow esox philosophiser..  You have no fear, because you are intimate with fear.  Don't listen to Snag, he goes to work with salmon juice on his pants, plus he eats harbour pike.  He's a very small, spiteful old jigga.  yyyeeee booyeee!  Welcome to my domain.  H to the D
Very Impressive. It looks like 1 pike is about 38 inches and the rest are over 40! Were they caught trolling or casting?
nice collection of fish there guys
Now those are some very impressive Pike caught over just a few days.   Great job guys.
When were those caught?  I assume recently.  the date on the pics are wrong obviously.  That was not January.  Nice fish!!
OK I read part one.  3rd Sat in May.  Nice
